name: Edificio Italia
description: Skyward wide angle view in front of Edifício Itália (Italy Building) in São Paulo. This skyscraper is famous for its rooftop restaurant with a scenic view of downtown (pictures of which the author also have taken). Date September 06, 2014. Coordinates 23°32'42.2"S 46°38'36.1"W.
